# Append-only shared logs: 3 parallel lanes + jeff all append rows to these files each
# cycle. Default git merge treats two appended tails as a conflict — with disjoint code
# ownership these logs are the #1 REMAINING conflict source. merge=union concatenates
# both sides instead of conflicting (safe for append-only files; do NOT add structured
# or hand-edited files like STATE.md / DECISIONS.md / assignments here).
.claude/agents/activity_log.md merge=union
.claude/agents/contributions/*.md merge=union
ci-debug/*.txt merge=union
ci-debug/*.md merge=union
NEEDS_YOU.md merge=union
